Description
-----------

The **alphazeroclamp** keyword prevents the alpha channel of this stage from tiling by forcing 100% opacity outside normalized UV coordinates.

Usage
-----

    alphazeroclamp

Parameters
----------

This keyword does not accept parameters.

Example
-------

Not available.

Notes
-----

The stage specific version of this keyword is used to override the effects of the global keywords...

